%N A321020 A hybrid of Kolakoski's sequence A000002 and Golomb's sequence A001462: if A001462(n) is odd replace it with 1, if even with 2.
%C A321020 This is A000002 rewritten so the run lengths are given by A001462.
%C A321020 The companion sequence, A001462 rewritten so the run lengths are given by A000002, seems to be A156253.
%C A321020 Note that Kolakoski's sequence A000002 and Golomb's sequence A001462 have very similar definitions, although the asymptotic behavior of A001462 is well-understood, while that of A000002 is a mystery. The asymptotic behavior of the two hybrids A156253 and A321020 might be worth investigating.
